        "details": {
            "description": "<p>This <em>mushroom ring</em> forms a portal to the First World, allowing the Thorned Monarch's reinforcements into the Material Plane. When the PCs approach, a creature emerges. Creatures continue to emerge until the mushroom ring is disabled. Disabling the mushroom ring also causes any creatures that have emerged to disappear.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:22](trained) or @Check[type:nature|dc:22] to rearrange the mushrooms to disrupt the portal (two actions) or <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dispel Magic]{Dispel Magic}</em> (2nd level, counteract DC 20) to counteract the magical properties; three successes are required to disable the portal</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
